('proj-exploratory-analysis-report', 'grp-data-wrangling-and-exploratory-analysis-application-review', 2, 'project', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Exploratory Analysis Report', 'Milestone project: Build a portfolio-ready deliverable for exploratory analysis report with implementation notes, verification evidence, and a concise explanation of tradeoffs.', 'checkpoint', 7, 'intermediate', '{"whatToBuild":"Build a portfolio-ready deliverable for exploratory analysis report with implementation notes, verification evidence, and a concise explanation of tradeoffs.","buildSteps":["Define the Exploratory Analysis Report scenario, target user or reviewer, and the specific Exploratory Analysis Review concepts it will demonstrate.","Define the business question, audience, grain, metric formulas, and decision the artifact should support.","Prepare or clean the dataset and document assumptions, exclusions, and data-quality checks.","Build the report, dashboard, notebook, or workbook with the minimum views needed to answer the question.","Validate the numbers against source rows, spot checks, or reconciliation notes.","Write a short interpretation with caveats and recommended next actions.","Keep the scope focused enough to complete, review, and explain the a Exploratory Analysis Report workbook, report, or dashboard with documented assumptions."],"nodeKey":"proj-exploratory-analysis-report"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Apply Data Cleaning, Data Visualization, Exploratory Data Analysis through a focused Exploratory Analysis Report artifact.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, workflow, or review decisions behind the project.","Validate the result with evidence that another person can inspect.","Document assumptions, limitations, and a concrete follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["The a Exploratory Analysis Report workbook, report, or dashboard with documented assumptions is available for review.","The Exploratory Analysis Report scope, setup path, input data or scenario, and expected outp