('proj-data-science-portfolio-capstone', 'grp-portfolio-capstone-core-practice', 2, 'project', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Data Science Portfolio Capstone', 'Capstone project: Build a portfolio-ready deliverable for data science portfolio capstone with implementation notes, verification evidence, and a concise explanation of tradeoffs.', 'checkpoint', 7, 'advanced', '{"whatToBuild":"Build a portfolio-ready deliverable for data science portfolio capstone with implementation notes, verification evidence, and a concise explanation of tradeoffs.","buildSteps":["Define the Data Science Portfolio Capstone scenario, target user or reviewer, and the specific Data Science Capstone Delivery concepts it will demonstrate.","Choose a coherent product or case-study scenario that can integrate the strongest projects from the roadmap.","Define the architecture, data or workflow model, user path, and review evidence before implementation.","Build the core artifact end-to-end with scoped features rather than disconnected demos.","Add validation evidence appropriate to the role, such as tests, metrics, query checks, playtest notes, traces, screenshots, or incident notes.","Prepare a case study explaining decisions, trade-offs, limitations, and what would need further review for real deployment.","Package the repository or artifact so another person can reproduce or inspect the result.","Create a review checklist that connects the artifact to the relevant skills and roadmap segment.","Write a limitation and risk section so the project is presented as reviewable evidence, not a certification claim."],"nodeKey":"proj-data-science-portfolio-capstone"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Apply Data Science Workflow, Data Storytelling, Portfolio Communication through a focused Data Science Portfolio Capstone artifact.","Integrate multiple roadmap areas into one coherent case study rather than isolated exercises.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, workflow, or review decisions behind the project.","Validate the result with evidence that another person can inspect.","Document assumptions, limitations, and a concrete follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["The a portfolio-ready Data Science Portfolio Capstone case study and integrated artifact is available for review.","The Data Science Portfolio Capstone scope, setup path, input data or scenario, and expected output are documented.","The main workflow runs or can be inspected through a notebook, repository, dashboard, prototype, report, configuration, or case study.","The case study connects implementation decisions to relevant roadmap skills and explains why alternatives were not chosen.","Validation evidence is included and directly relates to the project brief.","The notes identify trade-offs, limitations, and one next improvement without claiming mastery or job readiness.","The project is packaged so a reviewer can understand the artifact without live mentoring."]'::jsonb),
